description:
#RHONY may be off for the July 4th holiday this week, but Everything Iconic is not. We break down the Real Housewives of Dallas & Real Housewives of Orange County season trailers frame by frame. Hannah and Louis from Southern Charm Savannah also join us at the end to talk about their upcoming season.


*For bonus episodes, join the Patreon at Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
